<para style="q1">

<verse number="13" style="v" />Why does the wicked man reject God</para>

<para style="q1">and say in his heart, "You will not hold me accountable"?</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="14" style="v" />You have taken notice, for you always see the one who inflicts the misery and sorrow.</para>

<para style="q1">The helpless entrusts himself to you;</para>

<para style="q1">you rescue the fatherless.</para>
